# Security Policy

## Supported Versions

This project is a small static web application built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

There are currently no versioned releases.  
The latest version available in the repository is the only supported version.

---

## Reporting a Vulnerability

If you discover a security issue related to this project, please report it by opening an issue on this repository.

Please include:

- a clear description of the issue  
- steps to reproduce the problem  
- the affected file or feature, if known  
- any relevant screenshots or code references  

Thank you for helping improve the security and reliability of this project.